Hide settings and actions by pattern via product.json configuration

Adds excludedSettingPatterns and excludedActionPatterns arrays to product.json,
adds excludedSettingPatterns to the IProductConfiguration interface in product.ts,
and modifies configurationRegistry.ts to route pattern-matched settings to
excludedConfigurationProperties (hidden from the Settings UI).

